OL,3,GOrkney & Shetland
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FCloudy for
OL,6,FShetland with outbreaks of showery
OL,7,Frain throughout. Mostly cloudy for
OL,8,FOrkney with a few showers and some
OL,9,Fclearer intervals. Strong northerly
OL,10,Fwinds easing overnight.
OL,11,
OL,12,CSaturday:FFor Orkney, a largely dry
OL,13,Fday with sunny spells and just the odd
OL,14,Fshower possible. Cloudy for Shetland
OL,15,Fwith outbreaks of rain continuing
OL,16,Fthrough the day. Moderate
OL,17,Fnorthwesterly breeze.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
