OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Sunday to Tuesday:FCloudy
OL,6,Fon Sunday with rain spreading and
OL,7,Fclearing northeastwards. A few showers
OL,8,FMonday but generally drier with sunny
OL,9,Fspells. Cloudy with rain Tuesday.
OL,10,FModerate winds becoming strong on
OL,11,FTuesday.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
